{%- block heading %}
## SECTION {{ slNum }} (Maximum Marks: {{ maxMarks }}){.text-center}
{%- endblock %}

{%- block sectioninfo %}
- This section contains **{{ totalQuestions | toWords | upcase }} ({{ totalQuestions | zeroPad: 2 }})** questions.
{%- endblock %}
{%- block questioninfo %}
- The answer to each question is {{ questionInfoTypeMsg | default: "a **NUMERICAL VALUE**" }}.
{%- endblock %}
{%- block roundoff %}
{%- if decimalValueUpto %}
- if the numerical value has more than {{ decimalValueUpto | toWords | downcase }} decimal places, **truncate/round-off** the value to **{{ decimalValueUpto | toWords | upcase }}** decimal places.
{%- endif %}
{%- endblock %}
{%- block eachquestion %}
- For each question, enter the correct {{ typeMsg | default: "numerical value" }} corresponding to the answer using the mouse and the on-screen virtual numeric keypad in the place designated to enter the answer.
{%- endblock %}
{%- block markingscheme %}
- Answers to each question will be evaluated _according to the following marking scheme_:
  - |-----------------|---|-------------|
    | *Full Marks*    |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| {{ questionMarks.correct | prepend: "+" }} if **ONLY** the correct {{ typeMsg | default: "numerical value" }} is entered; |
    {%- if questionMarks.incorrect == 0 %}
    | *Zero Marks*    |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| 0 In all other cases. |
    {%- else %}
    | *Zero Marks*    |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| 0 If no value is entered (i.e., the question is unanswered); |
    | *Negative Marks* {.text-nowrap}|&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| {{ questionMarks.incorrect }} In all other cases. |
    {%- endif %}
    {.no-border}
{%- endblock %}
